ers have undoubtedly improved in the recognition, and the ability to participate in women</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">’</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s boxing, there is still considerable prejudice and opposition in the U.K which prevents women from fighting and earning a living.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">They are unable to have the opportunity to earn the large prize money available to the men</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Our former World flyweight champion REGINA HALMICH was able to become a millionairess in Germany where she attracted television audiences of over 5 million viewers on the ZDF </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">TV</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> channel.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">This opportunity is not open to British women because the BBC and SKY television channels will not televise their fights. We consider this to be sexual discrimination.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Similarly there is discrimination against women</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">’</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s boxing in the print media.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">I have experienced cases where SKY televised all the men's bouts at York Hall, Bethnall Green London, but deliberately omitted to screen the sole women's bout. The next day the published results in the Daily Telegraph omitted the women's bout!</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Without the oxygen of publicity, which television and the major print media should provide, promoters will not give women work.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">I enclose a copy of an article</span><a name="_ftnref1"></a><a href="#_ftn1">[1]</a><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> from The Yorkshire Evening Post Newspaper of Friday 2nd, February 2001 (OVER 12 YEARS AGO !) recording the Meeting which one of our World Title Challengers, MICHELLE SUTCLIFFE from Leeds had with the then Minister for Sport KATE HOEY MP in an attempt </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">to overcome the sexual discrimination which still persists.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">September 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div><hr style="width:33%; height:1px; text-align:left" /><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn1"></a><a href="#_ftnref1">[1]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt">Not printed.</span></p></body></html>